Mercedes Cabral (amuru August 10, 1986) bu onye omekorita nke Filipino
A maara ya nke ọma maka ịgbanye n'ụlọ nka Philippine na ihe nkiri nọọrọ onwe ya, ọkachasị ndị Brillante Mendoza dị ka Serbis, Kinatay, Captive, na Womb gị
Ọ pụtakwara na ihe nkiri South Korea akpịrị nkụ nke Park Chan-wook duziri
Na 2021, ọ pụtara na Huwag Kang Mangamba Ọ rụrụ ọrụ onye mmegide bụ isi Agatha, ajọ nne nnochi anya Joy, nke Francine Diaz na-egwu
Na 2016, ọ pụtara na onyinye Phil Giordano meriri obere ihe nkiri SUPOT
